          Learn more about my background, current work, and what makes me tick.
        </p>
      </a>

      <!-- Projects Card -->
      <a href="/projects" class="group block p-6 rounded-xl border border-vapor-purple/30 bg-vapor-darker/50 hover:border-vapor-cyan/50 hover:bg-vapor-darker/80 transition-all glow-box">
