          Check out what I've been building and the things I'm working on.
        </p>
      </a>

      <!-- Blog Card -->
      <a href="/blog" class="group block p-6 rounded-xl border border-vapor-purple/30 bg-vapor-darker/50 hover:border-vapor-magenta/50 hover:bg-vapor-darker/80 transition-all glow-box">
